    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>神如何使他們重生？</strong></p><p>神照著祂的大憐憫，藉耶穌基督從死裡復活，使他們重生。</p>",
