    "reference_id": 119843,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "彼得前書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>他們是藉著什麼蒙神大能保守的？  </strong></p><p>他們是藉著信心蒙保守，以得著那預備在末世要顯現的救恩。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "60001005",
