    "reference_id": 119846,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "彼得前書 1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>雖然信徒沒有見過耶穌，但他們做了什麼事？  </strong></p><p>他們愛祂，信靠祂，並以滿有榮耀的、難以言喻的喜樂歡欣不已。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "60001008",
