    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "彼得前書 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>那些信祂的人因着信心得到了什麼？</strong></p><p>他們得到了靈魂的救恩。</p>",
