    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>先知藉著他們的搜尋和探求，是在服事誰？</strong></p><p>他們是在服事信徒。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
