    "reference_id": 119855,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "彼得前書 1:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>寄居的選民從誰那裡學會了虛妄的行為？</strong></p><p>他們從他們的祖先那裡學到虛妄的行為。</p>",
