  {
    "content_id": 612485,
    "reference_id": 119859,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "彼得前書 1:23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60001023",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>信徒是如何重生的？  </strong></p><p>他們是藉著那不可朽壞的種子，透過那活潑常存的神的話語，而不是從那朽壞的種子重生的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "60001023",
          "start_ref_usfm": "1PE 1:23",
          "end_ref": "60001023",
