    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60003018",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>基督為什麼一次為罪受苦？  </strong></p><p>基督一次受苦，為要引領彼得和信徒到神面前。</p>",
