    "reference_id": 119887,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "彼得前書 3:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60003022",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>既然耶穌在天上坐在神的右邊，天使、掌權的和有權能的都必須做什麼？  </strong></p><p>他們都必須服從祂。</p>",
